snippet.title: Death Worm Gameplay
snippet.description:
A fun downloadable game (I take NO credit in making, producing, or touching this game, only in the fact that I play it). Just Google it to find it.

This is another "Common Round" to a game, so it is kind've long. After the wave of human forces, you face some...unique enemies.
